026572d2-b100-441b-b86f-f00fd499eaaa.do_description: To make the output, you have to...make different pattern figures using all colors but light blue
026572d2-b100-441b-b86f-f00fd499eaaa.grid_description: The output grid size...multiply the grid size by its own size
026572d2-b100-441b-b86f-f00fd499eaaa.see_description: In the input, you should see...a small grid with two objects

16c05fbe-89b3-4204-a607-427261cdbd35.do_description: To make the output, you have to...replace each of the colored squares on the input grid with the light blue pattern but in the color of the square, then orient the pattern to correspond with the colored squares in the new grid.
16c05fbe-89b3-4204-a607-427261cdbd35.grid_description: The output grid size...will be the size of grid with the light blue squares multiplied by the length of the grid with the light blue squares. So, for example, if the light blue squares are in a 4x4 grid, the output grid will be 16x16.
16c05fbe-89b3-4204-a607-427261cdbd35.see_description: In the input, you should see...some squares of various colors on one half of the grid and some blue square that make a pattern on the opposite side of the grid.

76a39e5c-d374-461a-aaeb-ba13fcedb4dc.do_description: To make the output, you have to...replace each of colored grid by light blue color grid pattern
76a39e5c-d374-461a-aaeb-ba13fcedb4dc.grid_description: The output grid size...will be size of light blue multiplied by number of blue grid
76a39e5c-d374-461a-aaeb-ba13fcedb4dc.see_description: In the input, you should see...6x3  grid size, first 3x3 grid will have same color and another 3x3 grid will have another multi color pattern

7d1d98fd-52bc-4c2b-971e-e551174760d4.do_description: To make the output, you have to...ignore the light blue, take the other colors, separate them and recreate the pattern of the light blue
7d1d98fd-52bc-4c2b-971e-e551174760d4.see_description: In the input, you should see...a small multicolor pattern
